The data are stored as:
 <ingroup root height>
    ├── <num loci>
    │   └── <replicate>
    │      ├── <theta>
    │      │   └── <num sites>
    │      │      ├── loci1.nex       # sequence data for the first gene tree
    │      │      ├── ...
    │      │      └── starbeast2.xml  # starbeast2 input file
    │      └── g_trees.trees          # the true gene trees     
    └── OG_s_tree.tree                # the true species tree
